content: First, we continue to have a very robust pipeline of 19 health plan prospects representing national, regional, and local health plans in all lines of business across the U.S. One large state plan has shared with us over 1.2 million lives in their data feed from which we were able to ascertain a significant opportunity greater than our existing customer base to improve the apparent unmet behavior health needs of their members which include a significant cohort of first responders.
